targets.expr:
(
  sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{le="0.256", job=~"$jobs", code!~"101|5.*"}[$interval])) by (job)
+
  sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{le="1.024", job=~"$jobs", code!~"101|5.*"}[$interval])) by (job)
)  
/ 2 / sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_count{job=~"$jobs", code!~"101"}[$interval])) by (job)
